  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t擦屁股纸共匪中国“刑法”垃圾又创新鲜玩意儿“等待”罪：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9XNlJUalBPLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/W6RTjPO.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/W6RTjPO.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/W6RTjPO.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n如今大陆中国各类“等待”罪略列—— <br/>\n<br/>\r\n《中华人民共和国<b>等待罪</b>列表》<br/>\r\n等待嫖娼<br/>\r\n等待强奸<br/>\r\n等待抢劫<br/>\r\n等待停车<br/>\r\n等待杀人<br/>\r\n等待行凶<br/>\r\n等待妄议<br/>\r\n等待盗窃<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/56497\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/56497\">等待放屁</a><br/>\r\n等待辱华<br/>\r\n等待打人<br/>\r\n等待谩骂<br/>\r\n等待滋事<br/>\r\n等待叛国<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/7491\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/7491\">等待CNM</a>...<br/>\r\n等待习近平<br/>\r\n等待戈多<br/>\r\n等待革命…<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\">乱世笑林</a>。 又见：<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/56497\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/56497\">中国放屁罪</a> <a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/58492\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/58492\">中国妄笑罪</a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9qZU1tTnc3LmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/jeMmNw7.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/jeMmNw7.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jeMmNw7.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
